{"surah": 99, "verses": [{"id": 1, "text": "إِذَا زُلْزِلَتِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَرْضُ زِلْزَالَهَا <span class=end>١</span>"}, {"id": 2, "text": "وَأَخْرَجَتِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَرْضُ أَثْقَالَهَا <span class=end>٢</span>"}, {"id": 3, "text": "وَقَالَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نس</tajweed>َ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>نُ مَا لَهَا <span class=end>٣</span>"}, {"id": 4, "text": "يَوْمَئِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ذٍ ت</tajweed>ُحَدِّثُ أَخْبَارَهَا <span class=end>٤</span>"}, {"id": 5, "text": "بِأَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ رَبَّكَ أَوْحَىٰ لَهَا <span class=end>٥</span>"}, {"id": 6, "text": "يَوْمَئِ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ذٍ ي</tajweed>َصْدُرُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َاسُ أَشْتَا<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>تًا ل</tajweed>ِّيُرَوْ<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> أَعْمَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>لَهُمْ <span class=end>٦</span>"}, {"id": 7, "text": "فَم<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>َن ي</tajweed>َعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ خَيْ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>رًا ي</tajweed>َرَهُۥ <span class=end>٧</span>"}, {"id": 8, "text": "وَم<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>َن ي</tajweed>َعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ةٍ ش</tajweed>َر<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ًّا ي</tajweed>َرَهُۥ <span class=end>٨</span>"}]}